@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-4">

    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <hr />

    <p>
        This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you visit or interact with this website. This policy applies to this demonstration application.
    </p>

    <h4>Information Collection</h4>
    <p>
        As this is a portfolio demonstration project, we do not actively collect or store any personal information from visitors. Any data entered into forms (such as the flight search) is used only for the duration of the session to demonstrate application functionality and is not saved.
    </p>

    <h4>Use of Information</h4>
    <p>
        The information processed by this application is for demonstration purposes only. It is used to simulate a real-world booking process and to showcase the technical capabilities of the ASP.NET Core framework. We do not use this information for marketing, analytics, or any other commercial purpose.
    </p>

    <h4>Data Security</h4>
    <p>
        While no real user data is stored, this project is built with standard web security practices in mind to demonstrate a professional approach to application development.
    </p>

    <h4>Contact Us</h4>
    <p>
        For any questions about this project, please refer to the project's source code and documentation on GitHub.
    </p>

</div> 